nodes.text: During the First Order/Resistance War, shortly after the Battle of Crait, General Leia Organa assigned Commander Poe Dameron and his team on a mission to Coronet City on Corellia, to participate in a secret auction of a decrypted list stolen from the First Order. The list contained names and locations of political prisoners being held in secret, along with other Resistance members wanted by the First Order.
